<item>
            <title>[LU-16413] T10PI is broken for CentOS 8.x</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16413</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The T10PI block integrity patches for lustre server kernel is broken, the bio_integrity_prep_fn interface is removed.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;As a result the autoconf feature test macro HAVE_BIO_INTEGRITY_PREP_FN was not defined, and the custom block integrity generate/verify was never enabled for CentOS 8.x&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The current block integrity generate/verify functions also require changes to be able to work on CentOS 8.x kernels.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
